      "isSplit": false,
      "description": "• Code is written\n• Unit tests and integration tests written and passing\n• Code reviewed by another developer\n• Basic testing of deployed code on DEV environment completed by developer\n• API documented on Confluence if appropriate\n• Code passes StyleCop / ESLint rules as appropriate\n• Code passes SonarQube rules (once we get this in place)\n• Code passes other static analysis, for instance Veracode (again, once we get this in place)\n• Comments for testers (if required) within the work item\n• If feature is flagged then enable flag in DEV and redeploy to re-run E2E Tests\n• Update e2e pipeline tests if needed\n• Any associated devops work is defined, completed, peer-reviewed and tested",
